text: The Baltic Open is a women's professional tennis tournament held at National Tennis Center Lielupe in Jūrmala, Latvia. It replaced the Moscow River Cup with the tournament joining the Women's Tennis Association (WTA) Tour with it being classified as an International tournament. It takes place on outdoor clay courts.
